        en: "Each product is linked to lot, date, shift, and work order. Evidence available for technical, commercial, or audit requests.",
      },
    },
    {
      n: "04",
      t: { es: "Verificación final", en: "Final verification" },
      d: {
        es: "Chequeo final con evidencia trazable. Se libera únicamente producto conforme a especificación.",
        en: "Final check with traceable evidence. Only spec-compliant product is released.",
      },
